TheQuietCorner_GCEF_2019_Grant

Garrison Children's Education Fund
April 16 at 9:25 AM ·

As the Saturday night that would have been our Spring Thaw at Bear Mountain Inn approaches, we are sorry to miss the annual opportunity to gather with each other to celebrate the wonderful families, students, and teachers in our town.

We hope the inspiring video, below, highlighting this year's upgrades and changes to Nurse Melissa's health office at GUFS will lift your spirits a bit during this challenging time:

https://vimeo.com/391870330

We look forward to seeing you in the near future and hope that all are faring well in this challenging time.
